[Intro – bar 1–8]  
Ney + tar (arpeggio) + engil daf ritmi + pianino pianissimo  

[Verse 1 – bar 9–24]  
Violin pizzicato + ney fon + tar frazalar  
Pianino F – Dm – Gm – C

[Chorus 1 – bar 25–40]  
To‘liq string’lar kiradi + daf kuchayadi  
Skripkalar legato, pianino kuchli arpeggio

[Verse 2 – bar 41–56]  
Xuddi 1-verse, lekin violalar yumshoq pad tarzida fonni ushlab turadi  

[Chorus 2 – bar 57–72]  
Birinchi chorus’dan ko‘ra kengroq. Skripkalar yuqori oktavaga ko‘tariladi. Choir pad kiradi.

[Bridge – bar 73–88]  
Tar + ney duo  
Cello’da d minor aralash modulatsiya, piano b/n melancholik chordlar

[Final Chorus – bar 89–104]  
To‘liq orkestr + tutti strings + pianino arpeggio  
Vokalda yuqoriga ko‘tarilish – kuchli dramatik final

[Outro – bar 105–112]  
Ney + tar + pianino solo. Sezilarli fade out.
